name: COVID19ICD10CMValueSetForPregnancy
title: COVID19 ICD10CM Value Set for Pregnancy
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to pregnant state.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes pregnant state and ectopic and other non-viable pregnancies.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes molar pregancies, conditions complicating pregnancy (e.g., Pre-existing essential hypertension complicating pregnancy), complications due to pregnancy (e.g., Pre-eclampsia) and maternal care for normal pregnancy and pregnancy related conditions. It also excludes terms related to labor, delivery, puerperium, and postpartum states.)
